James Ford (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Ford_(actor) 0 Alan Ford (born 23 February 1938) is an English actor. He is best known for his roles in the Guy Ritchie crime capers Snatch and Lock, Stock and Two Smoking Barrels, and from guest starring in The Bill.
